'''Iaphagena''' was the grandmother of [[Bria Tharen]]. [[Renn Tharen]], wanting to honor his mother and mother-in-law, but not wanting his daughter to be stuck with either of their names, combined the first syllables of their names, [[Brusela]] and Iaphagena, to make Bria.

